{
  "stem": "7093.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was the Neolog.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Neolog is something in between United Synagogue and Reform synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything was done in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Religious education-- religion was compulsory in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't be an atheist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you had to belong to some religion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a religious tax was deducted from everybody's salary, which went then to-- either to the synagogue-- but it was not one particular synagogue.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But-- I mean, yes, we belonged to the Neolog synagogue officially.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My parents never went to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But were had-- we were obliged to go to religion lessons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to-- and-- and I had very big difficulties with the religion teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because my brother was rather naughty, and also because I resented my parents not going to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a provincial town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this teacher, who was at the time 60 years old and-- and not very patient used to beat me constantly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and I just couldn't learn with him at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I failed my-- I-- I couldn't learn to read Hebrew, which was rather odd.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because later on, I became a Hebrew teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I-- I-- couldn't-- so I-- I did-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I failed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had two swat the whole summer to pass my exam in September.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would have been kept down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because religious education was a compulsory subject.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And if you didn't pass it, then you had to repeat the whole year in all the subjects again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Luckily, I passed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't have to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
